                      configuration file structure is different both for standalone
                      and clustered configurations. The
                      %a{:href=>'https://docs.jboss.org/author/display/AS7/Getting+Started+Guide#GettingStartedGuide-AS7AQuickTour'}"AS 7 Quick Tour Guide"
