                    %br
                    
                    %li
                      %dt
                        Caching
                      %dd
                        Infinispan provides the caching facility in JBoss EAP 6.  It replaces
                        JBoss Cache which is provided in JBoss EAP 5.  
                        There is no 1-to-1 mapping of the server configuration attributes 
                        between these two components, however the, 
                        %a{:href=>'https://docs.jboss.org/author/display/ISPN/Configuration+Migration+Tools'}"Configuration Migration Tools",
                        section of the, "Infinispan 5.2", guide provides directions for migrating the settings.
